The '''Winneshiek Players''' is an amateur [[Theatre|theater]] group in [[Freeport, Illinois]]. It was founded in 1916 and has offered a season of performances for every year since 1926. The Winneshiek Players claims to be the oldest continuously operating volunteer (amateur) theater group in the [[United States]].<ref>http://www.winneshiekplayers.org/Winneshiek%20History.htm</ref>

